  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img style="width: 812px; height: 435px;" src="/media/13086957/site_masthead.jpg?width=812&amp;height=435&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ed82abf8cf5f41c88fbd03bbd2cf69e1" /></p>
<h2 style="color: #003155;"><span>Ski Total's New Chapter</span></h2>
<p>Ski Total was founded nearly 40 years ago by two ski enthusiasts who wanted to share their love of the mountains and skiing with others. Ski Total grew into one of the best ski chalet specialists in the UK offering a comfortable ‘home from home’ experience which was informal, relaxed and with great food and service.</p>
<p>In 2021, Ski Total and sister ski company Inghams merged and came together under one brand. This was to combine the catered chalet experience that Ski Total did best, with the extensive choice of resorts, hotels, and apartments that Inghams offered. With 85 years of experience, Inghams continues to offer you amazing ski and snowboard holidays.</p>
<p>You'll enjoy an authentic catered chalet experience in one of Europe’s top ski resorts, with the same high quality service, welcoming atmosphere and tasty food - everything you know and love about Ski Total, but with your experience now being delivered by our expert Inghams team.</p>
