<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="color: #003155;">You’re in safe hands</h3>
<p><a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" target="_blank" title="In Safe Hands"><img style="width: 808px; height: 472px;" src="/media/13086945/homepage2-1.jpg?width=808&amp;height=472&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f07a0167a7f64f0cae145330c1b770da" /></a></p>
<p>When you book with Inghams, we’ve put in extra measures in place to help keep you and your money safe too. Find out more about our <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">Covid refund guarantee</a> and how we’re giving extra peace of mind for your next holiday.</p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
